{
  "stem": "23579.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We stayed in Wilno a couple of days, by friends of ours, two-- but they went away before us, to Wilno, And they gave us a room.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we stay only about four days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were telling us they're looking for the Bielskis in Wilno.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew that we ran away, you understand?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they're looking for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, right away, we left with the first [NON-ENGLISH]-- the first-- [NON-ENGLISH] not-- train-- what the-- in the wintertime, the oil and everything is going with that-- you know, for the-- for the heat, what they bring in from Poland-- in Poland.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oil?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Heating oil?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[POLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Coal.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And me and Lilke, and Tuvia, and Zus, were sitting on the coal, like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody should see us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, like that, we went to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Lublin, we came in Lublin already, somebody from the Aliyah Bet was waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, you are the Bielskis?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have something for the Bielskis.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Israel was not Israel, it was Palestine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he send you a letter that you have to come to Romania.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Romania will wait for you four certificates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you have to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But till the certificate came, took about six months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we stayed in Romania, in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did we go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The number 11-- everything with number 11.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We took a truck, we took a-- we took the-- whatever it took.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We crossed as Persian Jew-- not Persian-- Greek Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, this was so many people, they were going from one place to the other one, we didn't have a place where to sit.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my husband tore his coat-- he was always smart-- tore his coat, and he begin to [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- you understand what I'm talking to you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lice.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
